+    <title>TeAndrea Burnett Tutoring | 1st & 2nd Grade Tutor in Troy, Alabama</title>
+    <meta name="description" content="Teacher-owned 1st and 2nd grade tutoring in Troy, Alabama. Reading fluency, phonics, math fluency, and confidence-building support from an experienced classroom teacher." />
